text: General Khin Nyunt (; ; born 11 October 1939) is a Burmese military intelligence chief and politician. He was the 9th Prime Minister of Myanmar from 25 August 2003 until 18 October 2004, until he was arrested by his senior officers. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese generals Category:Prime Ministers of Myanmar
title: Khin Nyunt
